data.description: Discover a gem nestled in the heart of South Fulton! This stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is less than 3 years old and boasts a wealth of desirable features. Step inside to find a main-level bedroom with a full bath, perfect for guests or a home office.  The heart of the home is the beautiful kitchen complete with an island, ideal for meal prep and entertaining. Overlooking the family room, where a cozy fireplace invites relaxation.  Upstairs, a spacious loft awaits, surrounded by three generously sized bedrooms. The owner's suite is a sanctuary with its spa-like bath, offering a retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life.  Additional highlights include a full unfinished basement, a recently screened-in deck, and the privacy of a cul-de-sac location. With easy access to the interstate, commuting to work is a breeze.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this house your dream home!  **Professional Photos are forthcoming**
